The Electoral Commission (EC) in Uganda has blocked presidential candidate Robert Kyagulanyi, alias Bobi Wine, from campaigning in 16 districts without permission.
Bobi Wine had hoped to return to the districts he skipped in his campaign schedule but EC wants him to sign a memorandum of understanding (MoU) before he embarks on a return journey to the districts.



